query:
SELECT 
  e.id,
  e.category,
  e.amount,
  e.description,
  e.expense_date,
  b.name as branch_name
FROM expenses e
LEFT JOIN branches b ON e.branch_id = b.id
WHERE e.expense_date >= '2025-12-01'
ORDER BY e.expense_date DESC, e.category
LIMIT 50;
